Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,As Detective Conan welcomes its 15th anniversary...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:14.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We're going to whoosh and swoosh\Nthrough solving more cases this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please continue rooting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, an incident hasn't occurred yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's simply out cold from having too much toso sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Causing your eyelids to swell and permeating your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tear drops serve as a prelude to wealth of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mystery is hidden in the tennis court.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hit a decisive smash with shrewd reasoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:46.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,THE DEVIL HIDDEN IN THE TENNIS COURT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko's tennis coach, Gotou Takao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwas selected to participate in a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,North Karuizavva Plateau Resort Park
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:58.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,After being dragged along by Sonoko, who had come to cheer for him, we found ourselves in North Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:02:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you sure this is all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're only doing a practice match for the competition\Ntoday, so we'll be fine if we finish before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:31.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Gotou Takao (21)\NTennis Club Vice-Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:31.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsuchida Yuha (19)\NTennis Club Member
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:29.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,To think you'd bring that snotty lady\Nfrom the Suzuki Financial Group...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you up to!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's only here to cheer me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to ditch me for her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I care about a Iittle girl like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because she's from the rich Suzuki Financial\NGroup that I decided to do her a small favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the only treasure that fills my eyes, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it's always better to have a bigger fish to fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you dare betray me, I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} went?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, aren't you the girl who was with Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Mouri Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:29.35,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Azuma Fumihiro (22)\NTennis Club Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If it's about that boy, he went to the restroom a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:29.35,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Want me to check on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I should go myself then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only men can go in anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure looks like a spacious place, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the guy from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the money I lent you back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you wait a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:06.80,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ootake Chie (19)\NTennis Club Member
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If you can't return it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll be in deep trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to your support that I'm able\Nto participate in the competition, Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I have a match to get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a bothersome girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and keep donating money to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite the player...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't get my money back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the others are worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were just fighting not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Game, Gotou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, your honey lemon water like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, now we're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, Yuka knows me the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feel free to use this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coach Gotou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep up the great work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you know my favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because your racket is always that color, Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice play!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:06:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, senpai, I won't screw things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Captain Azuma is such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for his injury, his place in the tournament\Nwouldn't have been taken by Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you aren't up to par to be my opponent,\Nwhy don't we make it mixed doubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna team up with a rookie girl and give you a handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohf sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're having a doubles match next, so come team up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's putting us away and pairing with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coach Gotou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm honored to play with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be best if you took off your gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like Sonoko is doing quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai looks like he's not feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The collapsed male is Gotou Takao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 21 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the vice-captain of the college tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He collapsed during the practice match due to poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the hospital, his symptoms matched\Nwhat would be expected of aconitine derivatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} ingested the toxin lying around\Nsomewhere with his fingers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it, Inspector Yamamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,North Karuizawa is in Gunma Prefecture, so no wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't consider it an accident or food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:10:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doctors think he may have ingested the\Ntoxin 10 or 20 minutes before he collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a murder case targeting Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is not deceased yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's highly possible he was given poison\Nduring his match and then killed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, he isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This wasn't an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how did the culprit do it during the match\Nwhile surrounded by spectators on the tennis court?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These ladies gave Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} refreshments and supplies earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Refreshments?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps those refreshments were laced with the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ali right, go investigate the refreshments\Nand supplies as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hope you do your job right, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't get a positive tox reaction from the\Nbelongings of the relevant parties, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The refreshment and supplies consisted of a bottle, a towel,\Nand racket grip tape that all came back positive for toxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kitakaruizawa Plateau Resort ^ Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This, this, and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see this kind of scene in detective dramas, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I should try this for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you currently are a police detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:22.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,「3 ladies provided Gotou refreshments」 →
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The actions Gotou took during his break were like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:22.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,「Gotou Paired with Suzuki & shook hands」 →
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:22.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,「Touched towel, drink, and grip tape in\Nthat order on the bench」 →
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,「Wrapped hid racket with tape」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the match, I saw Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and\NTsuchida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} guarreling in the locker room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Tsuchida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dating, she suspected\Nthat he's courting Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} because she's rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, what did you mean by—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bearing a grudge because of that, Tsuchida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Ndecided to put an end to Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would a police officer seriously take a kid at his word?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsuchida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You offered Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the drink mixed with poison, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the toxin was found on the outside of the\Nbottle, the report showed the drink wasn't poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing how his palm was inflamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't he get that by holding the bottle laced with poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lady here talked to Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nalone in this very room earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chie here has been feeding Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}\Nher money in order to win his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the point she even gave away her tuition fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, if I can't find a way to pay my\Ntuition, I'll have to drop out college...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ootake{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you saturated the towel with poison\Nand offered it to him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he then wiped his face with the towel, the poison\Nwould enter the membranes of his eyes and nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the hospital, there was no\Npoison detected on Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took a sweeping victory at the\Nmatch and didn't even break a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't use the towel either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took it off his neck and left it on the bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't us, then it had to be the work of that\Nlady from the Suzuki Financial Group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it seems Senpai approached\Nher to attempt some gold-digging...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She uncovered his intentions and flew off the handle\Nbecause she really had been lavishing him with money, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't lavish anything on Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm only here to cheer him on because I\Nheard he was participating in a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Coach said he always changes his grip\Ntape before each game, I gave him one as a gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you say Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would change\Nhis grip tape before each game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth behind the case just hit me with a bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to present the solution to the tennis\Ncourt mystery at the tennis court itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to strap on the grip tape, you have\Nto first peel off the adhesive clear film on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:13:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you applied toxin to the film beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could get Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s hand poisoned because\Nhe would change his grip tape before each game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We received a report from forensics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the peeled film inside Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bag and\NSuzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s tennis glove, traces of poison were detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on Sonoko's tennis glove too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r} licked his fingers many\Ntimes because he couldn't peel off the film easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit applied poison to the film beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And offered it to him after putting the tape back into the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why there wasn't a positive tox reaction on her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:15:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} presented the poison-laced grip tape\Nto Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with the intent to murder him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko would never do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was peeling off the film...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He licked his fingers numerous times,\Ncausing his body to take in the toxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During his play, the toxin circulated inside him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he collapsed when he was about to serve the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your love relationship discord is your motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You told the handsome guy that you were\Nlovey-dovey with him, but you were betrayed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So your maiden feelings turned into hatred at some\Npoint, enabling your murderous intent to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll question you after we head to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, I said it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She might've had a crush on him but you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all the circumstantial evidence points to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a false accusation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I have to let Sonoko clear away\Nany misunderstanding with her own mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will the Gunma Police be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's she doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she imitating Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, you've got it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will now proceed to reveal the truth of this case to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the case already solved?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl over there is the culprit, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You applied poison to the grip tape's film and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s next match started immediately\Nafter he changed out the grip tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could the poison possibly be left on the towel and\Nbottle he touched prior to that if you were correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, you'd peel off the film with your fingertips...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s palm was inflamed due\Nto coming into contact with the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the poison got on his entire palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} grabbed something with poison laced all over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the culprit is Tsuchida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You applied poison to the bottle, and to avoid\Ncontact you handed it over by holding on its strap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the poison was from the bottle he grabbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd be unable to transfer the poison to the\Ntowel he touched before, wouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the culprit is Ootake{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} touched the towel around\Nhis neck, the poison got on his hand and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the skin comes into contact with poison, we\Nshould be able to see apparent symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ootake{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} passed the towel with\Nher bare hands, so that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, where could the poison be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, the tennis gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit wore poisoned gloves and shook hands with\NGotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, causing him to come into contact with poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the culprit is you as I suspected!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you're still alive and kicking after eating these cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Sonoko was called to the doubles match...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I high-fived Sonoko and touched her glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If any poison were on the glove,\Nit would've gotten on my hand too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since I used that hand to eat the\Ncookies, I would've been poisoned too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, where on earth did the poison come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we don't have any suspects left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another method remains in which one can make direct contact\Nwith Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} on the court and pass the poison onto him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something a tennis player would do naturally...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wouldn't be suspected even if under the audience's surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The captain!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in the stands the entire time and\Ndidn't offer him any refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I poison Gotou as he was on the tennis court?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You high-fived Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that instant, you forced the poison onto Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:19:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why my tennis glove had poison on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s palm had already come into\Ncontact with poison before shaking hands with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was none other than you who\Nhigh-fived him before our handshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were to apply poison to my hand, I\Nwould've been in serious trouble too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you had your tennis gloves on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Typically, only two balls are prepared in a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's considered proper etiguette to return a\Nball to the court if it flies into the stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Azuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s glove had poison on the palm side...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hit it with the back of his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, when it was switched to a mixed doubles match...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've been nervous to see me shaking hands\Nwith Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} after being called to pair with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the investigators detect poison from my gloves and suspect\Nsomeone from the stands held the source of the poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your effort would've gone down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be best if you took off your gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had me take off my gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I left them on the bench, they could be taken\Naway during the confusion of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply impressed by your deductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Or I would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where's the evidence!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the evidence, as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Inspector Yamamura kicked\Nover the ball container just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only one of the balls didn't bounce at all\Nwhich gave me a strange feeling about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This ball has an odd rift on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After committing the crime, Azuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took off\Nhis gloves and stuffed them inside that ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in order to not have the ball stand\Nout, he hid it among the other balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He plotted to get rid of it after the commotion had died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If these gloves have Azuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s fingerprints\Non them and test positive for poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll serve as the decisive evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, are you saying that the credit is all mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a kind man like you do this, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to participate in the competition tomorrow but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was jealous of me and deliberately tripped me during practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike senpai, I'll never tumble and fall over like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my leg fractured, I had to give up competing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Gotou took my place instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think my participation was robbed\Nby a low-down womanizer like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thanks to him, my sponsor contract\Nand scholarship went to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one guy that I'll never forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such the suspicion on Sonoko was promptly cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, Gotou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} regained consciousness at the hospital and\Nhis prognosis looked positive, according to Inspector Yamamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.10,0:23:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deduction Queen Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you would be made into the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so worried, so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, you really are my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that said, it is case closed, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too much, Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Case closed my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a detective drama, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:23:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her grudge about being a suspect is indeed frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan was brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:19.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ganguro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.40,0:24:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:24.37,Signs,,0,0,0,,LOOK FORWARD TO THE NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Our ten-week long\Nsweepstakes is\Ncoming to an end\Nnext week!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:24.37,Signs,,0,0,0,,We await your\Nentries!
